    "description": "官方QQ群：785687499<br><br>《我是黄油》是一款画面卡通化且精美的通关游戏，它无时无刻不在挑战着你的智慧和耐力，要做到屡战屡败的准备方能通关游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/6e61e8c36971eeeef50e934488117a74.poster.avif?t=1697601169\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/6e61e8c36971eeeef50e934488117a74.webm?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/6e61e8c36971eeeef50e934488117a74.mp4?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>想象一下，化身为小黄油在厨房、快餐店等常见场景，动用你的智慧以及耐力一步一步跳向终点！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/c965d7ee54a5b7091ee4b669e7754b3b.poster.avif?t=1697601169\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/c965d7ee54a5b7091ee4b669e7754b3b.webm?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/c965d7ee54a5b7091ee4b669e7754b3b.mp4?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>平时随手可拿的瓶瓶罐罐，在你面前都成为了遥不可及的高山峻岭！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/c74ca0590a3d19687178cfb9ffe9be5b.poster.avif?t=1697601169\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/c74ca0590a3d19687178cfb9ffe9be5b.webm?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/c74ca0590a3d19687178cfb9ffe9be5b.mp4?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>平时你看不起的小动物，在这里都能主宰你的命运！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/899e40eaa9ff7cadd7b018e1e370cc6a.poster.avif?t=1697601169\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/899e40eaa9ff7cadd7b018e1e370cc6a.webm?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/899e40eaa9ff7cadd7b018e1e370cc6a.mp4?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>平时令你催延三尺的食物，却在此时成为你通关的障碍！ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/6f8bddcbc41a904667a79b77e5466f56.poster.avif?t=1697601169\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/6f8bddcbc41a904667a79b77e5466f56.webm?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859180/extras/6f8bddcbc41a904667a79b77e5466f56.mp4?t=1697601169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>-只用跳跃和控制方向达到目的地。<br>-每个关卡看起来很简单，但要达到目的地远没有你想的那么容易，路途中总会有不一样的惊喜在等着你！<br>-根据内部测试，平均关卡通关时间为2小时，最快通关时间为5分钟，来挑战下，接受挑战！<br>-失恋？失业？在这里都是小事儿，去体会一下你不曾接受过的挫折！<br>-条件允许多准备几个手柄，条件不允许好好调整心态哦。<br>-每个场景都有不一样的彩蛋，看看你能找到几个！<br>-这游戏都能通关，人生没有迈不过去的坎！漫画！多有趣！",
